"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-05-17-olympic-hopeful-facing-deportation-jamaica-canada-rejects-familys-asylum-claim\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Jamaican-born standout athlete is facing deportation from Canada after a removal order was issued to his family on Monday by the North American country's Border Services Agency.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9988364579565282, \"rank\": 0.001078659771606794, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999232894085359, \"rank\": 7.666370155742352e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamarri Lindo, 20, a former Kingston College athlete who is now enrolled at York University in Toronto, says his impending deportation is putting a damper on his hopes of representing Canada at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Thames_Colleges_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999389424393, \"rank\": 5.945745737148854e-08, \"text\": \"Kingston College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Thames_Colleges_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Thames_Colleges_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9999999917590685, \"rank\": 7.269928809854387e-09, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}, {\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9988364579565282, \"rank\": 0.001078659771606794, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A top-ranked sprint hurdler at the collegiate level, Lindo was set to compete at the Olympics trials in May.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My goal was to make the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, it feels like everything is being taken away,\\\" Lindo told Toronto'sCTV News.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I could have a mental health breakdown.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My heart is sinking,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tamarri Lindo with his family, including dad George, who are facing deportation from Canada.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9988364579565282, \"rank\": 0.001078659771606794, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo and his family arrived in Canada in April 2019, following which Lindo's father, George, filed a refugee claim for political asylum.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 851, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9988364579565282, \"rank\": 0.001078659771606794, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to George, the family was targeted by gangs in Jamaica because of his political work, which included him mobilising support for the People's National Party.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999855199660207, \"rank\": 1.447983698619064e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Party_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9641434262210193, \"rank\": 0.03718934652471597, \"text\": \"National Party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Party_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Party_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The asylum claim outlined several occasions in which the family was subject to violence, including a 2012 election incident in which George's neck had been slashed.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However their asylum claim has been rejected three times, with the Canadian authorities noting that they were ineligible for asylum on humanitarian and compassionate grounds.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9595091224994087, \"rank\": 0.042168445001918076, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In rejecting the Lindo's application, Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada said that the violence experienced by the senior Lindo could not be directly linked to his political activism.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The agency further argued that crime, including murder, is widespread throughout Jamaica, noting that the risks faced by the family were shared by all persons living in Jamaica.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999855199660207, \"rank\": 1.447983698619064e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999855199660207, \"rank\": 1.447983698619064e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}]}"